data.description: Welcome to 44 Breton Avenue! This uniquely fun ranch style home features 3+ bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, kitchen pantry, offers one floor living, heated indoor in-ground pool & hot tub, loft, finished basement and attached 2 car garage! In your spacious backyard you will find 2 separate patios spaces, apple & pear trees, and a 10x30 shed offering plenty of room for extra storage! Wooden beams, cathedral ceilings, hardwood floors, and cozy wood stove add to its charm! Located in a neighborhood close to schools, soccer fields and the Mousam Way Trail! This is truly an unforgettable home; reach out to set up your showing today!
